{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1a2ff480a9","title":"毛泽东同邓小平关于批评“四人帮”的一次谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f02321a1ef","index":0,"year":1975,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"1a2ff480a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"6917f1f9b0","name":"陈锡联","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"8e2c446eb1","name":"王洪文","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bae4b55cdd","type":"title","text":"同邓小平关于批评“四人帮”的一次谈话（节录）毛泽东（未经本人审阅，未与邓小平核对）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"6cbf758875","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：会议的情况［注：指一九七五年五月三日主席在政治局会议上批评“四人帮”以后，政治局根据主席指示开会批评“四人帮”的会议。］毛主席都知道了。）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"f8791e8745","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛点头）我看有成绩。把问题摆开了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"558b993f3d","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：最后他们否认有“四人帮”。）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"9a4c8cfec8","type":"paragraph","text":"过去有功劳，反刘少奇，反林彪。现在就不行了，反总理，反邓小平，反叶帅，反陈锡联。要告诉庄则栋，有事要找陈锡联，不要跑王洪文、江青，不然陈锡联不好办事。你（指邓）跟庄则栋讲一下，告诉他，不找陈锡联不好。跑江青、王洪文，司令不好办。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"56e4724296","type":"paragraph","text":"风向快要转了，在政治局。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"f62d73dcfb","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：政治局的同志气很大，我说不要把话都说完，散了。）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"e5ff0bdb0c","type":"paragraph","text":"这个办法好，留有余地。大家清楚就行了。我准备找王洪文谈，叫他找你（指邓），听你的话。他威望不高。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"66e28389a3","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：他最后的发言，政治局许多同志感到不真实。）","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"73091008fb","type":"paragraph","text":"江青也不喜欢他，专门在我这里告他的状。他应该好好工作。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"be3c9ab2b4","type":"paragraph","text":"没有大问题。你要把工作干起来。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"f41fad1353","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：这方面我还有决心就是了。）那好。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"2d88d8da34","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：反对的人总有，一定会有。）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"c109624678","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛笑）木秀于林，风必摧之。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"5f776174e2","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：开始工作时，主席给我这个工作岗位，我说主席是把我放在刀尖上了。）","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"465de7c900","type":"paragraph","text":"这是叶帅提议的，我赞成的。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"d75e44c0a2","type":"paragraph","text":"（邓：总参谋长。）","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"c069b3e0c1","type":"paragraph","text":"就是这样。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"},{"id":"1a1ee5d406","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：这是中央办公厅秘书局提供的唐闻生、王海容的记录稿。文中的注是原有的。）","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9"}],"page":{"id":"9bd918f591","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"1a2ff480a9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}